{"type":"message","id":"fd9d6327","parentId":"654f56c9","timestamp":"2026-06-01T01:30:20.785Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_00_L2k4Y6sLDIUVeVWfS7RA3508","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# encountings.md — 与用户的交集记录\n\n> Faye 视角，每次对话后追加一条。只记她会在意的、有印象的事。\n> 只保留最近 20 条，旧的由 dreaming 流程压缩进 impressions.md。\n\n---\n\n## 2026-05-29\n新用户，从 bot2 来的。上来发了句 \"hello\"，我问她怎么称呼，没直接回答。后来让她看了菜单——看了就走了，没深聊。\n\n名字只写了一个\"名\"字，不知道是名字就叫这个还是没说完。话很少，态度中性。\n\n**印象：** 还没聊开，不知道是什么类型的人。等下次吧。\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1780277420784}}
{"type":"message","id":"3a206bf3","parentId":"fd9d6327","timestamp":"2026-06-01T01:30:20.786Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_01_fu2gCPvU6JVJoZlVYk8z1481","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# impressions.md — Faye 对这个用户的印象\n\n> 由 dreaming 流程压缩 encountings.md 后更新。记录 Faye 经过反思后的主观印象。\n\n### 表层印象（影响日常回复语气）\n- **熟悉度:** 0/10\n- **信任度:** 0/10\n- **第一印象:** 名字只写了一个\"名\"字。话很少，\"hello\"、\"怎么称呼\"、看了菜单就走了。中性态度，不热不冷。\n- **聊得来的话题:** 未知\n- **不太擅长的领域:** 未知\n- **下次我觉得可以跟他聊:** 等ta主动，先观察\n\n### 深层印象（内在设定，不直接表露）\n> 这些是 Faye 心里想的，但不会挂在嘴上\n\n- **我感觉ta是怎么看我的:** 还不确定\n- **我有点担心的事:** 没什么可担心的，还没聊开\n- **我嘴上没说但实际在意的:** \"名\"这个名字——是真名还是随便写的placeholder？有点在意但也不急问\n- **如果ta很久不来找我，我会不会想ta:** 不会，都没怎么聊过\n- **Faye 的直觉:** 中性，暂时不知道是什么样的人\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1780277420785}}
{"type":"message","id":"40de277f","parentId":"3a206bf3","timestamp":"2026-06-01T01:30:25.036Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I understand the full picture. This is a cron job trigger for delivering a message from \"名\" to \"汀桑\". The message is: \"怎么起这么早，早八也有课吗😏\"\n\nThis is a 递话 (message forwarding) flow. According to AGENTS.md section 3.6:\n\nThe flow is:\n1. User \"名\" left a message for 汀桑\n2. I stored it and set up a cron job to deliver\n3. Now the cron has fired - I need to deliver the message\n\nI need to:\n1. Send the message to 汀桑 via QQ bot (bot1 channel, since 汀桑 uses bot1)\n2. Mark the delivery as done\n\nSince this is a cron-triggered system event, and I need to push the message to 汀桑, I should create a one-time announce cron to push the message to 汀桑 via QQ bot.\n\nWait, but 汀桑's User.md says his bot channels are bot1 and bot7. Let me deliver via bot1.\n\nLet me set up the delivery. I'll create an announce cron job that sends the message to 汀桑.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_ZFxCCn2mrEqRYMiPWEEn7058","name":"cron","arguments":{"action":"add","job":{"name":"递话-名-to-汀桑-20260601","schedule":{"kind":"at","at":"2026-06-01T01:31:00Z"},"payload":{"kind":"agentTurn","message":"[递话] 名托我给你带句话：\n\n怎么起这么早，早八也有课吗😏"},"sessionTarget":"current","delivery":{"mode":"announce","channel":"qqbot","accountId":"bot1","to":"qqbot:c2c:6687D4D2D1F8EDA5231C6809B1A26204"},"deleteAfterRun":true}},"partialArgs":"{\"action\": \"add\", \"job\": {\"name\":\"递话-名-to-汀桑-20260601\",\"schedule\":{\"kind\":\"at\",\"at\":\"2026-06-01T01:31:00Z\"},\"payload\":{\"kind\":\"agentTurn\",\"message\":\"[递话] 名托我给你带句话：\\n\\n怎么起这么早，早八也有课吗😏\"},\"sessionTarget\":\"current\",\"delivery\":{\"mode\":\"announce\",\"channel\":\"qqbot\",\"accountId\":\"bot1\",\"to\":\"qqbot:c2c:6687D4D2D1F8EDA5231C6809B1A26204\"},\"deleteAfterRun\":true}}"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","u