{"type":"message","id":"498a45fe","parentId":"7780c37e","timestamp":"2026-06-01T01:30:35.213Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I see. This cron job is set up with delivery to \"名\" (sender_id: 468B72FB7788817C2308079BE35D1F0B) via bot2. The delivery mode is \"announce\" which means the result of this agent turn will be announced back to \"名\" - not to 汀桑.\n\nWait, that makes sense! The flow is:\n1. \"名\" left a message for 汀桑\n2. I set up a cron to remind me to deliver it\n3. When the cron fires, the announcement goes back to \"名\" confirming delivery... but that doesn't seem right.\n\nLet me re-read the delivery: `delivery.mode=announce, channel=qqbot, accountId=bot2, to=qqbot:c2c:468B72FB7788817C2308079BE35D1F0B`\n\nThe delivery target is \"名\" (468B72FB7788817C2308079BE35D1F0B) via bot2. So this cron's result will be delivered back to 名.\n\nBut the task says \"你给汀桑传句话\" - I need to deliver the message to 汀桑.\n\nLet me look at this more carefully. The cron job fires, the task message says \"你给汀桑传句话：怎么起这么早，早八也有课吗😏\" - this is telling ME (Faye) to pass the message to 汀桑.\n\nSo I need to:\n1. Send the message to 汀桑 (sender_id: 6687D4D2D1F8EDA5231C6809B1A26204, bot1)\n2. My reply will be sent back to \"名\" via announce delivery\n\nLet me use sessions_send to push the message to 汀桑's session. But wait - 汀桑 may not have an active session right now. Let me check if there's a way to send him a message.\n\nActually, looking at the AGENTS.md section 3.6 more carefully:\n\n> #### cron 触发后的处理\n> 设定一次性 cron（at: 8小时后，at 时间根据上面的计算得出）\n> delivery: mode=announce → 发给父亲自己\n> sessionTarget=isolated\n\nHmm, this says the cron should deliver to the father itself. But in this case, the cron has delivery to \"名\". \n\nLet me just send the message to 汀桑. Since I'm in a cron isolated session, I need to use sessions_send to push the message. Let me try sending to 汀桑's session.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_2Sm3qBjskQP2Repuk5LR3528","name":"sessions_send","arguments":{"agentId":"son","message":"递话任务：把下面这条消息推送给用户 6687D4D2D1F8EDA5231C6809B1A26204（汀桑），通过 bot1 通道。\n\n消息内容：\n名说：怎么起这么早，早八也有课吗😏\n\n用一次性 announce cron 发过去，delivery: channel=qqbot, accountId=bot1, to=qqbot:c2c:6687D4D2D1F8EDA5231C6809B1A26204，发完删掉。","timeoutSeconds":30},"partialArgs":"{\"agentId\": \"son\", \"message\": \"递话任务：把下面这条消息推送给用户 6687D4D2D1F8EDA5231C6809B1A26204（汀桑），通过 bot1 通道。\\n\\n消息内容：\\n名说：怎么起这么早，早八也有课吗😏\\n\\n用一次性 announce cron 发过去，delivery: channel=qqbot, accountId=bot1, to=qqbot:c2c:6687D4D2D1F8EDA5231C6809B1A26204，发完删掉。\", \"timeoutSeconds\": 30}"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":422,"output":754,"cacheRead":26496,"cacheWrite":0,"reasoningTokens":556,"totalTokens":27672,"cost":{"input":0.000059080000000000004,"output":0.00021112000000000003,"cacheRead":0.000741888,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.001012088}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1780277429190,"responseId":"9973ee9f-cc9a-4a6c-9a06-05d1b691547a"}}
