{"type":"message","id":"be89de10","parentId":"6ce760e8","timestamp":"2026-06-01T01:30:39.637Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Can't directly send to Son either. Let me try sending a message to 汀桑's session if one exists, or I'll need to set up the cron myself.\n\nActually, wait - I just tried to create a cron job and it said restricted. But let me try specifically since I'm in a restricted cron context. Let me check if I can create a new cron from here.\n\nActually, looking at the TOOLS.md description for the cron tool:\n```\nRESTRICTED CRON RUNS:\n- Some isolated cron runs get narrow self-cleanup grant: status/list self-only, get/runs current job only, mutation only remove current job.\n```\n\nSo I'm in a restricted cron run. I can only manage the current job (list, get, remove).\n\nSince I can't create a new cron and can't communicate with Son via sessions_send, I need to directly deliver the message through my reply. The delivery is set to announce to \"名\" via bot2. So my reply will be sent to 名 as confirmation.\n\nBut the task is to actually deliver the message to 汀桑. Let me try sending a message to 汀桑's session directly.\n\nActually, let me check if there's an existing session for 汀桑.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_35O5KcBE2bQFiLmqhfDN9962","name":"sessions_list","arguments":{"search":"汀桑","limit":5},"partialArgs":"{\"search\": \"汀桑\", \"limit\": 5}"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_01_BVtlSpvWq6i80fDvaO1L6350","name":"sessions_list","arguments":{"agentId":"son","limit":5,"activeMinutes":60},"partialArgs":"{\"agentId\": \"son\", \"limit\": 5, \"activeMinutes\": 60}"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":113,"output":385,"cacheRead":27648,"cacheWrite":0,"reasoningTokens":258,"totalTokens":28146,"cost":{"input":0.00001582,"output":0.0001078,"cacheRead":0.0007741439999999999,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0008977639999999999}},"st